        <updateDate>2020-04-06T14:31:39Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Accelerate Long-term Investment Growth Now Act or the ALIGN Act</b></p> <p>This bill makes permanent the expensing of certain new business equipment. <em>Expensing</em> allows the deduction of the full amount of an expense item in the same taxable year. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
